flowchart LR
    Client[Client] --> CDN[CDN] --> LB[Load Balancer] --> API[API Gateway]

    API --> IdemRedis[(Redis Idempotency Cluster)]

    IdemRedis --> AuthOrch[Auth Orchestrator]
    AuthOrch --> AuthWrite[Auth Write Service]
    AuthOrch --> AuthRead[Auth Read Service]

    AuthOrch --> ServiceDiscovery[Service Discovery]
    AuthWrite --> ServiceDiscovery
    AuthRead --> ServiceDiscovery

    ServiceDiscovery --> Consul[Consul]
    ServiceDiscovery --> Eureka[Eureka]

    AuthOrch --> ConfigServer[Config Server]
    AuthWrite --> ConfigServer
    AuthRead --> ConfigServer
    ConfigServer --> ConfigRepo[(Central Config Repo)]

    AuthOrch --> Vault[Vault]
    AuthWrite --> Vault
    AuthRead --> Vault

    AuthWrite --> OTP[OTP Service] --> Notify[SMS / Email Gateway]

    AuthWrite --> CircuitBreaker[Circuit Breaker] --> OAuth[Google / Apple / Enterprise SSO]

    AuthWrite --> Kafka[Kafka]
    Kafka --> Audit[Audit Service]
    Kafka --> Fraud[Fraud Service]
    Kafka --> Analytics[Analytics Service]
    Kafka --> AsyncNotify[Async Notification Service]

    AuthWrite --> ShardRouter[Shard Router]

    ShardRouter --> WriteShard1[(User Write DB Shard 1)]
    ShardRouter --> WriteShard2[(User Write DB Shard 2)]
    ShardRouter --> WriteShard3[(User Write DB Shard 3)]

    WriteShard1 --> ReadReplica1[(User Read DB Replica 1)]
    WriteShard2 --> ReadReplica2[(User Read DB Replica 2)]
    WriteShard3 --> ReadReplica3[(User Read DB Replica 3)]

    AuthRead --> ReadCache[(Redis Read Cache Cluster)]
    ReadCache -->|MISS| ReadReplica1
    ReadCache -->|MISS| ReadReplica2
    ReadCache -->|MISS| ReadReplica3

    ReadReplica1 --> ReadCache
    ReadReplica2 --> ReadCache
    ReadReplica3 --> ReadCache

    AuthRead --> TokenStore[(Redis Token Cluster)]
    OTP --> OTPStore[(Redis OTP Cluster)]